\boldsymbol\Sigma = \begin{bmatrix}  \boldsymbol\Sigma_{11} & \boldsymbol\Sigma_{12} \\  \boldsymbol\Sigma_{21} & \boldsymbol\Sigma_{22} \end{bmatrix} \quad
